[11:43:00] [INFO]   DW 'bare' band captures impervious concrete/asphalt (ferry aprons, parking)
[11:43:00] [INFO]   in addition to actual bare soil — which is why port areas score high.
[11:43:00] [INFO]   The restricted-zone Overpass filter only checks patch CENTROID containment,
[11:43:00] [INFO]   so patches whose centroid is just outside a port polygon slip through.
[11:43:00] [INFO]   Fix → tighter water threshold (0.10 for NYC) or polygon-overlap test.
